==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reboil
<hw>Re*boil"</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧*boil")</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>boil</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>rebouillir</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To boil, or to cause to
boil, again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: To make or to become hot.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some of his companions thereat <qex>reboyleth</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir T. Elyot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reborn</ent>⟦br⟧
